{"tid":58213,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有朋友屋企人唔見左 各位巴絲幫下手","createTime":"2016-12-28T15:43:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T16:07:02.000Z","uid":5116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a1038232ea9b235462eae73872ae221978ddcee","tid":58213,"uid":5116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:43:52.000Z","msg":"請廣傳‼️‼️<br />\n幫忙留意有冇見過這個婆婆：<a href=\"https://notfound.collaction.hk/r/189\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnotfound.collaction.hk%2Fr%2F189&d=iO0XYmeTfJspZEcTWR7kw2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=dcd9f742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://notfound.collaction.hk/r/189</a><br />\n<br />\n衣著外表：👚👖👠<br />\n深色衣服，黑色鞋，腰間常揹著黑色腰包。身形非常瘦小，頭髮花白，皮膚白，戴黑色眼鏡，沒有戴錶。 <br />\n<br />\n事發：<br />\n2016年12月28日約七時離開家中（天水圍天悅邨），然後失去聯絡，電話通但無人接聽。 <br />\n她原本打算到坑尾村取車（白色面包車），然後行駛至旺角砵蘭街，但她朋友表示未有在旺角見到她，曾致電亦無人接聽。 <br />\n<br />\n平日晚上約六時至七時左右，她便會致電家人，七時左右到家，但今日全日沒有音訊。 <br />\n<br />\n🚨🚨🚨<br />\n如有人見過此人，請儘快聯絡警署，或親屬周燕琳：66072061 /90453825 /94734411。 <br />\n謝謝！"},{"pid":"7dc11642ce81f9fb9702f0006d6e84ad9ba5a88f","tid":58213,"uid":5479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:44:24.000Z","msg":"希望快啲搵番<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57542247a7ae898409293f12c7b9ad2f2a9a4408","tid":58213,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:44:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"997a9d2febe154660fbe8c4470464d7b78b012a4","tid":58213,"uid":5116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:45:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人妻咁快手好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54aa1443686b33a4cef99f299a865582dce14b61","tid":58213,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:46:23.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n希望快啲搵返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7aae337ebac98f1c2ca6dbbcecc00ffef9b7eca","tid":58213,"uid":5116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:46:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>希望快啲搵番<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希望啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f0e6c7aa1f378007e8cd9d84062c013d5ba13d","tid":58213,"uid":5116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:48:10.000Z","msg":"update:<br />\n嬤嬤沒有老人痴呆症，只是有點腳傷要拿拐杖走路，平日早上會由坑尾村車場取車(白色面包車)駛到旺角，晚上七時回家。<br />\n車牌：UB2234<br />\n*車場有紀錄嬤嬤上午9:20左右開車離開，然後連同面包車一同失縱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"851fae3180bea0170f357eca39b6ca3e4071887d","tid":58213,"uid":63976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:48:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"839e084cdbc4b416b42c8a972265eb4efebff803","tid":58213,"uid":53978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:50:15.000Z","msg":"推 天寒地涷希望快d搵得返"},{"pid":"f2f4e6dff9622c3e682231a60be90bb26b6a7372","tid":58213,"uid":5116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:50:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"470f598f043f59233872d5f1a42519cf9c46d4d1","tid":58213,"uid":5116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:52:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b63cd55f0d53254693f34219cc2d2cedaf956e3","tid":58213,"uid":5116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:54:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d12d7607ad45a4ad1c74577cb4bc7b5ab2ad11e","tid":58213,"uid":5116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:59:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a11b8710322f73ab56721874a7077eff73d4de2b","tid":58213,"uid":5116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:02:20.000Z","msg"